
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-you-idr-bgp-vpn-discovery-00.txt'>
    <title>"BGP VPN Peer Discovery Method", Jianjie You, Qiandeng Liang</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-you-idr-bgp-vpn-discovery-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document proposes a VPN peer discovery method based on BGP.  All BGP peers need to establish sessions with a centralized control point which collects and distributes BGP VPN Peer information according to local policies or filtering policies subscribed from BGP peers. Thereafter, the BGP node can select the interested peers with the same VPN services to establish sessions.  This would avoid unnecessary session between uninterested BGP peers.</description>
    <dc:date>2014-09-15T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
